text: Iványi may refer to: *Béla Iványi-Grünwald (1867–1940), Hungarian painter, member of the Nagybánya artists' colony, founder of the Kecskemét artists' colony *Gyula von Iványi (1864–1920), Hungarian Olympic fencer *István Szent- Iványi (born 1958), Hungarian politician and Member of the European Parliament for the Alliance of Free Democrats *Iványi (river), a tributary of the Zagyva in northern Hungary
title: Iványi
